{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WiN1hShkve91CkmpU7dEsL","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Learned Patterns\n     2→\n     3→## GitHub Authentication\n     4→- Always export GH_TOKEN from .env before running gh commands:\n     5→  ```bash\n     6→  export GH_TOKEN=$(grep GH_TOKEN /path/to/.env | cut -d= -f2)\n     7→  ```\n     8→- Cannot `--add-reviewer` when token owner is the PR author (HTTP 422)\n     9→\n    10→## Session Flow\n    11→- First session bootstraps repo, creates issues from PRD as `proposal`\n    12→- Cannot implement until issues are labeled `approved` or `ready`\n    13→- Focus on housekeeping when blocked: organize project board, update memory\n    14→\n    15→## Environment\n    16→- Find agent-browser with: `which agent-browser`\n    17→- Git remote uses PAT in URL: `https://ghp_...@github.com/<owner>/<repo>.git`\n    18→- Git remote URL may lose PAT between sessions — re-set with `git remote set-url`\n    19→- Must set `git config user.email` and `user.name` each session if not set globally\n    20→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5a1dc2c-f130-4d23-b0e6-5a47e7e3bcfa","uuid":"2af9d672-0c6d-41b8-8223-9d5af226051c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T11:24:15.076Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/app/.claude-beat/memory/patterns.md","content":"# Learned Patterns\n\n## GitHub Authentication\n- Always export GH_TOKEN from .env before running gh commands:\n  ```bash\n  export GH_TOKEN=$(grep GH_TOKEN /path/to/.env | cut -d= -f2)\n  ```\n- Cannot `--add-reviewer` when token owner is the PR author (HTTP 422)\n\n## Session Flow\n- First session bootstraps repo, creates issues from PRD as `proposal`\n- Cannot implement until issues are labeled `approved` or `ready`\n- Focus on housekeeping when blocked: organize project board, update memory\n\n## Environment\n- Find agent-browser with: `which agent-browser`\n- Git remote uses PAT in URL: `https://ghp_...@github.com/<owner>/<repo>.git`\n- Git remote URL may lose PAT between sessions — re-set with `git remote set-url`\n- Must set `git config user.email` and `user.name` each session if not set globally\n","numLines":20,"startLine":1,"totalLines":20}}}
